title: Vox Machina Ep. 61 - Denizens of the Moonbrush
description: As Vox Machina head into the Moonbursh they are drafted into of battle between a pack of Lycans and a Village of Pixies. Also, they make a pit stop at the Last Campsite of Sorudun the Happy. Everything goes well, obviously.
